About us

Delhi Rajasthan Transport Co. Ltd. Began business in 1971 as Associated forwarder in Rajasthan, operating as a domestic forwarder. From the beginning, the Company found a special niche in offering highly personalized and flexible services that were not offered by competitors. Today, DRTC is a $25+ million turnover company operating in Rajasthan , Gujarat , Haryana, Maharashtra , Tamil Nadu, Punjab, Karnataka , Andhra Pradesh and Kerala with 160 offices of its own…
